title: DAZ3D - Promo Style Catch Lights for Iray
description:
A pretty set of 25 portrait lights for DAZ Studio Iray, featuring 12 Eye Captures to further customize your lights, and 5 additional scaling options for the Eye Capture choices.

What's Included and Features

Promo Style Catch Lights for Iray (.DUF):

12 Catch Light Options
25 Light Presets
12 Transparency Maps (up to 800 x 800)

42 Lights: 

05 Catch Light Scale Options

Textures Include: 

DAZ Studio Light Presets for Iray (.DUF)
